            {
              "title": "Launch & training (final 40%)",
              "description": "We go live when you’re happy. You’ll get a personalised walkthrough video showing exactly how to edit everything, plus a tidy handover checklist (SEO basics, analytics, redirects if needed). The final 40% is invoiced before launch/handover."
